{'date': '2025-09-21T14:43:00+00:00', 'title': "Bihar 2025: From Nitish's twilight to a new political dawn", 'body': 'On an evening in a village dalan, an old uncle, who proudly says he has voted in more than seven or eight Bihar assembly elections, smiled and said with quiet certainty: "Ye Chanakya nahi,', 'url': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/blogs/voice-of-plebs/bihar-2025-from-nitishs-twilight-to-a-new-political-dawn/', 'image': 'https://static.toiimg.com/imagenext/toiblogs/photo/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Saurabh-Raj.png', 'source': 'The Times of India'}
{'date': '2025-09-22T06:13:00+00:00', 'title': 'Bihar Assembly election dates likely to be announced soon, CEC Gyanesh Kumar to visit state', 'body': 'The Election Commission is planning to hold the Bihar Assembly elections between Durga Puja and Diwali, with voting likely to take place between October 2 and October 29. This time, elections are expected to be conducted in two to three phases,', 'url': 'https://www.cnbctv18.com/india/politics/bihar-assembly-election-dates-likely-to-be-announced-soon-cec-gyanesh-kumar-to-visit-state-19682835.htm', 'image': 'https://images.cnbctv18.com/uploads/2025/02/delhi-election-reuters-2025-02-b7fecacd617f3a1b390d05088b712ec8.jpg?im=FitAndFill,width=500,height=300', 'source': 'CNBCTV18'}
{'date': '2025-09-22T06:29:00+00:00', 'title': 'Bihar elections likely in 3 phases from November 5-15: Report', 'body': 'The Bihar Assembly elections are expected to take place in three phases from November 5 to 15, following the Chhath Puja festival.', 'url': 'https://www.newsbytesapp.com/news/politics/bihar-polls-after-chhath-puja-voting-in-three-phases-november/story', 'image': 'https://i.cdn.newsbytesapp.com/images/l99220250922112933.png', 'source': 'NewsBytes'}
{'date': '2025-09-21T17:50:00+00:00', 'title': "BJP Alleges Abuses Hurled At PM Modi's Mother Again During Tejashwi Yadav's 'Bihar Adhikar Yatra'", 'body': "BJP alleges RJD workers abused PM Modi's late mother during Tejashwi Yadav's 'Bihar Adhikar Yatra', sparking outrage as Bihar heads toward crucial assembly elections.", 'url': 'https://www.msn.com/en-in/news/India/bjp-alleges-abuses-hurled-at-pm-modi-s-mother-again-during-tejashwi-yadav-s-bihar-adhikar-yatra/ar-AA1MZ7Kb', 'image': 'https://feeds.abplive.com/onecms/images/uploaded-images/2025/09/21/f6b1780040cb117135de97557ce522bb17584337656181163_original.jpg?impolicy=abp_cdn&imwidth=1200', 'source': 'ABP News'}
{'date': '2025-09-22T09:34:00+00:00', 'title': 'Assembly polls in Bihar to be held in three phases', 'body': 'The Bihar Assembly elections 2025 are scheduled to take place after Chhath Puja, with voting expected to be held in three phases from November 5 to November 15, according to sources familiar with the matter.', 'url': 'https://newstodaynet.com/2025/09/22/assembly-polls-in-bihar-to-be-held-in-three-phases/', 'image': 'https://newstodaynet.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/qrn58m6_election-commission_625x300_26_March_24.jpeg', 'source': 'News Today'}
{'date': '2025-09-21T19:30:00+00:00', 'title': "Lalu Yadav's Daughter's Post Sparks Fresh Family Feud Rumours Ahead Of Bihar Polls", 'body': "Rohini Acharya's posts on Sanjay Yadav's growing clout spark fresh rift in Lalu Prasad Yadav's family, weeks before Bihar polls, putting RJD's unity under spotlight amid rising political tension.", 'url': 'https://www.msn.com/en-in/autos/photos/lalu-yadavs-daughters-post-sparks-fresh-family-feud-rumours-ahead-of-bihar-polls/ar-AA1MZdwJ', 'image': 'https://feeds.abplive.com/onecms/images/uploaded-images/2025/09/21/4653f49e927431724ef199fe15e7ecfe17584397867321163_original.jpg?impolicy=abp_cdn&imwidth=1200', 'source': 'ABP News'}
{'date': '2025-09-22T05:40:00+00:00', 'title': 'Bihar elections likely to be held after Chhath Puja in 3 phases from November 5-15', 'body': 'A big election scoop from Bihar suggests voting for the new assembly is likely to happen in three phases after Chhat Pooja, between the 5th and 15th of November. The new assembly must be formed before the 22nd of November.', 'url': 'https://www.indiatoday.in/elections/assembly/video/bihar-elections-likely-to-be-held-after-chhath-puja-in-3-phases-from-november-5-15-2791198-2025-09-22', 'image': None, 'source': 'India Today'}
{'date': '2025-09-22T08:28:00+00:00', 'title': 'Bihar Poll Dates 2025 Likely Set Between Nov 5-15: What Voters Should Know', 'body': 'Bihar Assembly elections 2025 are scheduled between November 5-15. Check key dates, political alliances, voter list updates, and NDA vs INDIA bloc seat details.', 'url': 'https://www.oneindia.com/india/bihar-poll-dates-2025-likely-set-between-nov-5-15-what-voters-should-know-7867515.html', 'image': 'https://imagesvs.oneindia.com/img/2025/09/bihar-polls-1758529678.jpg', 'source': 'Oneindia'}
{'date': '2025-09-22T06:51:26+00:00', 'title': 'Bihar polls likely in 3 phases from Nov 5', 'body': 'Bihar is likely to go to polls in three phases from November 5 to 15, sources said, as the term of the current Assembly is set to end on November 22, 2025. The Election Commission is required to complete the election process before that date.', 'url': 'https://www.msn.com/en-in/politics/government/bihar-polls-likely-in-3-phases-from-nov-5/ar-AA1N2pNb', 'image': 'https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AA1N2hQZ.img?w=1500&h=800&m=4&q=79', 'source': 'Khabargaon'}
{'date': '2025-09-22T06:41:43+00:00', 'title': 'Bihar Election Likely After Chhath Puja, Diwali, Dates Out After Dussehra', 'body': 'Dates for the 2025 Bihar Assembly election will likely be announced after Dussehra (on October 2, this year) with the voting itself spread across two phases in the first and second weeks of November,', 'url': 'https://www.msn.com/en-in/politics/government/bihar-election-likely-after-chhath-puja-diwali-dates-out-after-dussehra/ar-AA1N2DpZ', 'image': None, 'source': 'NDTV'}
